  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nAfter reading https://crbug.com/chromium/1247389, I discovered that a very similar attack can be performed by a Chrome App using `chrome.fileSystem.chooseEntry` [0] and setting the `suggestedName` to an environment variable name.  \n  \n[0]: https://developer.chrome.com/do"
